      "actionDate": "2026-06-18",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Improving Travel for Military Members Act</strong></p><p>This bill allows the Transportation Security Administration (TSA) to establish a pilot program to expedite access to security screening for traveling active-duty military personnel and accompanying family members.</p><p>In selecting airports to participate in the pilot program, TSA must give priority to airports in proximity to certain military installations.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-07-08T17:27:15Z",
      "versionCode": "00"
    }
